    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to truly enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Seriously, you won't find a scratch on it. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in top-notch shape, this is the one for you. I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so let's get you behind the wheel!",
