    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. Power is delivered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced for structural longevity. The chassis remains taut with original bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the exterior retains its factory depth and luster. No deferred maintenance; a turn-key masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "2022 Performance Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Full service history included.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
