      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and is truly spotless inside and out. If you've been looking for that 'brand new' experience without the brand new price tag, you've found it! I'm happy to answer any questions or have you over to take a look in person. Let's get you behind the wheel of your dream car!",
      "price": 43500.0,
