    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is an impeccable E46 M3, a true collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit displays exceptional mechanical health with recent Blackstone oil analysis reports and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The high-revving powerplant breathes through six individual throttle bodies, delivering linear torque across the entire power band. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from preventative rear subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec suspension refresh utilizing Bilstein B6 dampers. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. All factory VIN tags are present, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is a turnkey machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
